d 'KLDBRECODE': module that provides crosswalk tables for translations between German KldB and ISCO. 
d
d  kldbrecode provides crosswalk tables for translations between
d German KldB and ISCO. The recodings can be performed using the
d crosswalk command by Ben Jann. The package allows for various
d transformations from German KldB codes: KldB 2010 to KldB 1988,
d ISCO-08, BIBB occupational fields and BAS occupational prestige.
d KldB 1992 to KldB 2010, KldB 1988, ISCO-88 (minor groups) and
d BIBB occupational fields. KldB 1988 to KldB 2010 and BIBB
d occupational fields. KldB 1975 to KldB 1988. ISCO-08 to KldB 2010
d and BIBB occupational fields. 
d
d KW:  KldB 2010
d KW: KldB 1992
d KW: KldB 1988
d KW: ISCO-08
d KW: ISCO-88
d KW: Berufsklassifikation
d KW: Classification of Occupations
d
d Requires: Stata version 14 and crosswalk, moremata from SSC (q.v.)
d
d Distribution-Date: 20250406
d
d Author: Hans Gerhardt , WZB Berlin
d Support: email hans.gerhardt@@wzb.eu
d
d Author: Anneke Kappes, WZB Berlin
d Support: email anneke.kappes@@wzb.eu
d
